---
title: Shawarma Spiced Turkey and Couscous with Apricots and Spiced Chickpeas
description: Simple Mediterranean flavours come together in the most blissful way in this dish. Fresh and light veggies, couscous and chickpeas fill you up without bringing you down! Add creamy yogurt raita, and you have a winner!
